#

Sweet Potato Soup

40 min
$8.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A creamy and comforting sweet potato soup, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • onion: 1 medium
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
